<h1>Unsubscribe from Amalgam Magazine</h1><br/>
<p>If you wish to be removed from a mailing list for any reason, please email <a href="mailto:mailinglist@amalgammag.com">mailinglist@amalgammag.com</a> with the email address you used to subscribe and mention that you would like to unsubscribe. If you are signed up for both mailing lists, please let us know which of the lists you would like to be removed from.</p>